{"TopicId":127622,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"What should I add to my Space Sation?","CreatedByName":"Dfthu","CreatedById":80296,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T00:56:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dfthu","CreatedById":80296,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T00:56:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I built this Space Station and I don\u0027t what\u00A0else I should add. I Have kerbals, science, fuel, power, ore and more! I need ideas!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/Aqpbx/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T01:01:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have a cupola module placed where you can get a really good view of whatever you\u0027re orbiting?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cantab","CreatedById":104935,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T01:11:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEngines, so it can go places.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speeding Mullet","CreatedById":62635,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T02:06:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEmergency re-entry pods in case it goes Kraken-tastic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Choctofliatrio2.0","CreatedById":154657,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T02:11:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA big truss with docking adaptors of all sizes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike Speeding Mullet said, reentry pods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA module with a bunch of mini probes attached to go out, do research and come back\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn orbital tug to carry spacecraft to the station\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T02:54:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd an asteroid mining section.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T04:26:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA klaw, so you can dock with things that have no docking capability. (Klaws are sooo much better than docking adapters! I don\u0027t see why people don\u0027t realize that.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaarst","CreatedById":126740,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T04:34:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222319108\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449894388\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA klaw, so you can dock with things that have no docking capability. (Klaws are sooo much better than docking adapters! I don\u0027t see why people don\u0027t realize that.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou want to know why we don\u0027t use the Klaw ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFollow these steps:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nMake a new save\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOrbit something with a Klaw on it\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOrbit another vessel with no docking port on it and rendez-vous with the first one\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDock the second vessel to the first one, using the Klaw, while still controlling the second\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLook in the direction of the ground\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is why we don\u0027t use the Klaw.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t want to do this, then here is what will happen:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbin simply disappears. Nothing more, nothing less.\u00A0This since whenever the Klaw was added.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd this is only one of the many bugs bound to the Klaw...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust remember: Klaw = Kraken magnet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxL_1023","CreatedById":152317,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T04:58:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMOAR BOOSTERS!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeriously though, you do need engines of some type. If you docked a cluster of fuel tanks and a NERVA you could probably get that to the Mun, Minmus or even Duna/EVE orbit with enough fuel. The acceleration is small enough to mitigate structural risk, while unlike ions you will actually see your velocity meter moving.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can set it up with a mobile processing lab and move it from SOI to SOI as you run out of data.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T05:44:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd a Mobile Research Lab, stick two Scientists inside and start doing orbital research \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T17:01:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuild another...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bigyihsuan","CreatedById":29291,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T17:49:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222319710\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449939691\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140061\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CliftonM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, CliftonM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuild another...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen dock it to the first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T17:52:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222319769\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449942554\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002229291\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bigyihsuan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, bigyihsuan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen dock it to the first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYES!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T20:24:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222318903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449882683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104935\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cantab\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, cantab said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEngines, so it can go places.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s what I was about to say. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T21:23:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222319130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449896329\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152317\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxL_1023\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, MaxL_1023 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMOAR BOOSTERS!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDang, someone beat me to it...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut some SRBs... that could be fun. Haven\u0027t used \u0027em much in orbit for anything other than deorbiting spent stages in an uncontrolled fashion, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrMarlboro","CreatedById":150717,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T21:37:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA diner with cupolas all around so the patrons can get a good view of everything there is, then place that diner right above the drive section so you can sell tickets to watch a controlled explosion with snacks. No refunds.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PineCone","CreatedById":151931,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-12T21:55:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222318903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022127622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221449882683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104935\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cantab\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, cantab said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEngines, so it can go places.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd some probes that can go down and mine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Taowulf","CreatedById":149037,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-13T00:44:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou need a ball pit.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhy isn\u0027t there a mod for that yet? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MalfunctionM1Ke","CreatedById":71626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-13T07:29:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess it is not about what to add, but maybe you want to put in another shape.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy first Spacestation looked quite similar:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022R3H5Xux.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/R3H5Xux.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut then I watched some Youtubers that influenced the way I put my sations together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(You have to think about the Picture without the giant Refueler and the two Landers attached to it)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WFYryez.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/WFYryez.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll in all, finding different designs \u002B re-designing my Space-Stations made it quite an adventure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy design is by far not superior. but I like that it is very versatile.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt holds enough Fuel to supply the small nuclear drive at the bottom and you could exchange the Com-Dishes for something else if you would like as they are just docked to the Station.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can detach the Dishes, the Solar Arrays and the drive stage if you would like.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just wanted to put out some ideas \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-13T07:39:50Z\u0022 title=\u002212/13/2015 07:39  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 13, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by MalfunctionM1Ke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SR","CreatedById":154209,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-26T19:16:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuild another in orbit of somewhere other than Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr just build a base.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AbacusWizard","CreatedById":116476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-26T20:13:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know what your space station really needs?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSPACE DISCO!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-D_JWKQ6O5vo/VLxy57hGUJI/AAAAAAAABTI/rGsNeta0c34/s640-Ic42/screenshot725.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot725.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-26T21:48:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt needs ALL the science. I recommend that you install four science labs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nich","CreatedById":145678,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-01-27T04:50:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA ring (if you love it put a ring on it)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}